sun.jvm.hotspot.ui.tree

Class SimpleTreeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.ui.tree.SimpleTreeModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.swing.tree.TreeModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleTreeTableModel

    public class SimpleTreeModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.tree.TreeModel
    A very simple tree model which allows the root to be set, so we can reuse the same model for various types of data; the specialization is contained within the nodes. This tree model operates on SimpleTreeNodes.
